data.description: Exquisite Victorian Gem: Historic Charm Meets Modern Comfort. Stamped concrete pathways lead to a picturesque wrap-around porch, welcoming you to this timeless beauty. Boasting 4 bedrooms plus a den/bonus 5th bedroom or home office. Enter through the grand foyer to discover a formal dining room exuding old-world charm, ideal for hosting cherished gatherings and celebrations. The heart of the home lies within the expansive kitchen, featuring double ovens, stainless steel appliances and a delightful bonus dinette area where mornings begin with warmth and comfort.  The family room is adorned with a charming fireplace and stone accent wall, setting the stage for cozy gatherings during colder evenings.  The finished basement has ample storage with radiant heat and bar.  Enjoy 2 full baths which cater to practicality and luxury. Outside, you will find a tranquil coy pond, large patio, carport and solar panels. This historic treasure harmonizes vintage elegance with modern sustainability.
